{"tid":1379664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報海外版：民陣「港獨」屬性暴露無遺","createTime":"2019-07-28T23:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T00:31:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"17b79bf73242c241165de4ca1462b34a6243a64c","tid":1379664,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1471075_1_20190729065724.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1471075_1_20190729065724.jpg&h=dd9192e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人民日報海外版發表署名文章，表示絕不允許裡應外合搞亂香港。<br />\n<br />\n文章作者為中國國際問題研究院國際戰略研究所副所長蘇曉暉，他在文章表示，民陣日前去信61個駐港總領館和辦事機構，呼籲對香港發出旅遊警示，認為旅遊業如果經歷「寒流」，埋單的是香港民眾，指「民陣」的「港獨」屬性再次暴露無遺。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，「港獨」勢力企圖挑動外部勢力干預香港事務、對中央政府和特區政府施壓，「民陣」請求外國對香港發佈旅遊警示，是處心積慮「拉外援」，認為香港民眾要擦亮眼睛，防範像「民陣」這樣的勢力引狼入室、禍國殃民。中國絕不允許有關勢力「裡應外合」，危害香港發展，踐踏「一國兩制」。"},{"pid":"4b22e1b343157aa74f50d6b08b18f9e92d1f92b7","tid":1379664,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:13:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471075-20190729.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471075-20190729.htm&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=434bb51b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471075-20190729.htm&h=e1e3e70c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471075-20190729.htm</a>"},{"pid":"38a467f3f317ba02fd2ca438b382c5843b6b5fa1","tid":1379664,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50d27802fb4504c21d50bbc908bbebf2faebc79","tid":1379664,"uid":289946,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:30:30.000Z","msg":"又港獨，真係好洗